273
00:18:58,525 --> 00:18:59,944
Do you think Socrates knew

274
00:19:00,527 --> 00:19:01,654
that in the future,

275
00:19:01,737 --> 00:19:05,157
his teaching method would throw us
into this state of terror?

276
00:19:06,909 --> 00:19:09,245
