didn't look scared.

277
00:19:09,328 --> 00:19:10,537
They seemed to enjoy this.

278
00:19:10,621 --> 00:19:13,040
If Joon-hwi passed the second round,
why is he here?

279
00:19:13,123 --> 00:19:15,000
No one gets dropped out at the interview.

280
00:19:15,084 --> 00:19:16,293
Jealousy equals defeat,

281
00:19:16,377 --> 00:19:19,171
